Title: Relates to the repair of certain bridges and other structures located on or adjacent to the Palisades Interstate Parkway
Summary: Relates to the repair of certain bridges and other structures located on or adjacent to the Palisades Interstate Parkway; directs the Palisades Interstate Park Commission to select a stone for bridge repair by December 1, 2023.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to the repair of certain bridges and other structures located on or adjacent to the Palisades Interstate Parkway
